  "detailed_description": "This game involves continuously defeating generated enemies to survive.<br><br>When you defeat enemies, you have a chance to obtain gems, coins, or boxes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793360/extras/e354ab6a585ca9617ffc5611b9048f06.poster.avif?t=1721068676\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793360/extras/e354ab6a585ca9617ffc5611b9048f06.webm?t=1721068676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793360/extras/e354ab6a585ca9617ffc5611b9048f06.mp4?t=1721068676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Accumulating gems allows you to level up, and upon leveling up, you can randomly acquire weapons or skills.<br><br>Each weapon or skill has seven levels, and reaching level 7 makes them overwhelmingly powerful.<br><br><br>There are two types of boxes: one grants passive abilities, and the other is a golden box that provides random weapons and skills, similar to leveling up.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793360/extras/06cdeb52b54f9e8b860719bbd1e5b4bc.poster.avif?t=1721068676\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793360/extras/06cdeb52b54f9e8b860719bbd1e5b4bc.webm?t=1721068676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793360/extras/06cdeb52b54f9e8b860719bbd1e5b4bc.mp4?t=1721068676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can use collected gems to enhance abilities in the shop.<br><br>Additionally, collecting coins allows you to unlock new characters or obtain stronger equipment.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793360/extras/d837a7a569997ff8c52d196b3e2028a3.avif?t=1721068676\" width=580 height=326 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793360/extras/395cbd78983832eee2bb24cd050abfd4.avif?t=1721068676\" width=580 height=326 /></span><br><br>The game features multiple stages, starting with normal difficulty, and upon clearing all stages, you can challenge the hard difficulty.",
