lass=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793360/extras/d837a7a569997ff8c52d196b3e2028a3.avif?t=1721068676\" width=580 height=326 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793360/extras/395cbd78983832eee2bb24cd050abfd4.avif?t=1721068676\" width=580 height=326 /></span><br><br>The game features multiple stages, starting with normal difficulty, and upon clearing all stages, you can challenge the hard difficulty.",
